reviewText: Gracias por mandarme el dvd rapido! lo que no me gusto fue la pelicula.

I like the fact that the movie is funny because of the situational irony portrayed in it. The movie is a romantic comedy. My favorite character is the one played by the child actor Octavio Ca~nas. However, I give the movie a score of 3 for its unnecessary use of bad language.
Silvia Navarro is excellent in this movies as usual. I loved her actuation, and enjoyed very much the movie. I highly recommend it.
